'''''From a Whisper''''' ni firime yikinamico yo [[Kenya|muri Kenya]] yanditswe kandi iyobowe  Wanuri Kahiu<ref>https://variety.com/2010/film/reviews/from-a-whisper-1117943881/</ref> . Iyi filime yakiriye nomination 12 kandi yatsindiye ibihembo 5 muri African Movie Academy Awards muri 2009<ref>https://www.wmm.com/catalog/film/without-a-whisper/</ref>, harimo ''Ishusho'' Nziza, ''Amajwi Yumwimerere''  '', Umuyobozi'' mwiza, ''Amashusho yumwimerere meza'' na ''AMAA Achievement muguhindura''<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/films/from-a-whisper/</ref> .  Iyi filime kandi yatsindiye igihembo ''cyiza cyo kwerekana inkuru nziza'' mu iserukiramuco rya Pan African Film &amp;amp; Arts 2010<ref>https://mubi.com/films/from-a-whisper</ref>,  kandi ihabwa igihembo cya BAFTA / LA ''Festival Choice'' Award 2010<ref>https://www.worldcat.org/title/from-a-whisper/oclc/495994211</ref>.  Nubwo iyi filime yibuka isabukuru yimyaka 10 ry’iterabwoba ryabaye ku ya 7 Kanama muri Kenya mu 1998<ref>https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/from_a_whisper_2009</ref>, ntabwo ivuga ku gisasu cy’iterabwoba. Iyi filime yerekana inkuru ifatika y’inyuma y’icyo gisasu<ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/us/film522498.html</ref>, ifata ubuzima bw’abahohotewe n’imiryango yabo bagombaga gutora ibice by’ubuzima bwabo byangijwe n’icyo gisasu.<ref>https://www.trigon-film.org/en/directors/Wanuri_Kahiu</ref>  

